## 📌 Overview

This project demonstrates how to analyze human behavior in real-time using **Ultralytics YOLO**.  
It processes live video streams or recorded footage to detect and interpret human activities.

---

## 🔧 Features

- Real-time human detection  
- Activity/behavior recognition  
- Video stream processing (webcam / CCTV)  
- AI-based monitoring system  
- Easy integration with dashboards or alerts  

---

## 🧠 Technologies Used

- Python  
- Ultralytics YOLO (YOLOv8 or later)  
- OpenCV  
- NumPy  

